class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tAdvance Siemens PLC and touch screens offer simple recipe changes, error detection, and real-time monitoring, making adjustments and troubleshooting a breeze.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-786a36ea e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"786a36ea\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-52da31d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"52da31d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3408790a e-grid e-con-full e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3408790a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-42c21c4a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"42c21c4a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-73368325 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"73368325\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Machine main parameters<\/p>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e607eff elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2e607eff\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.npack.com.cn\/allproducts\/monoblock-filling-capping-machine\" target=\"_blank\" monoblock=\"\">Vial Filling and capping machine <\/a><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-75c94e87 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"75c94e87\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6a603853 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6a603853\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>All in all, automatic monoblock liquid filling, inner plugging, and screw capping machines are your go-to for streamlined, high-quality packaging\u2014especially when you\u2019re aiming for space savings and operational efficiency.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e610314 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e610314\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The capacity of this monoblock one is according to the number of the filling nozzles and capping heads, max speed can reach 80pcs \/min.. This flexibility allows you to match production requirements, whether you\u2019re working with a compact setup for limited space or scaling up to meet higher demand.<\/p><table width=\"409\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"182\"><p><strong>Model<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td width=\"227\"><p>NP-MFC<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td width=\"182\"><p><strong>Filling Nozzles<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td width=\"227\"><p>1 , 2 or 4Nozzles<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td width=\"182\"><p><strong>Capping heads<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td width=\"227\"><p>1 or 2<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td width=\"182\"><p><strong>Production Capacity<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td width=\"227\"><p>1800-4800BPH<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td wid